reviewText: This movie is amazing! It definitely beat my expectations. I was a little surprised when I was watching the movie because I expected certain parts to be different from what they were. For example, I thought the main characters would fall in love and there would be that cliche sex scene after they landed on top of each other but no. That was one of the few examples that surprised me. Overall a great movie, I'm happy to use this as a starting point for my Asian Blu ray movie collection.
Been looking for this film on bluray and finally found it here. This is one of my favorite films. Love how it captures the city of Taipei.
